reviews.review:
I drove past Anne's Shop while driving past Springvale Shopping Centre. I called Anne to ask if she could help my pre-teen daughters with shaping their eyebrows. I had tried to shape them but couldn't make them even and had visited other salon's but was not happy with the service. She was friendly and accommodating and so I booked an appointment. My kids were nervous, but she was engaging and friendly and did such an amazing job with their brows! When they walked out, the difference to their faces was incredible. The shape of their brows lifted their faces, and it was done within minutes.

Highly recommended Anne! She knows her craft, and I am so thankful that I found her.

AA++ (Springvale location)
